[Q2] If that version of me walked into a room right now how would you know it was her She's going to walk with a lot of confidence with a lot of impact with a lot of humility at the same time pride that she was able to do something for the world that didn't exist up until now and create a product that is actually changing life through technology in a way that was not possible before

[Q3] Where is one place you most need your future self to show up in your business in a conversation I think one place where I need my future self to show up is the past version of me where go get attitude a sales that you're ready to make and finding the real need to make that impact and sell a product So I think from a business standpoint a good salesmanship is something that I want my future self to show up with

[Q4] Staying where you are has actually costed me an opportunity of risk but this has also come because of a lot of risk taking and lessons learned previously And probably it's been amazing in the sense that I've been moving and a more cautious self but I think the free spirited to get back up this question is now probing me to get back that risk levels in some ways

[Q5] What would you have to stop believing about yourself for the next version to be possible That the crazy ambitious free spirited driven girl is actually more fun than a cautious lessons learned risk girl So I guess you know go back to being the carefree version of you','[object Object]','2026-06-03 17:05:39.647+00','2026-06-13 17:05:39.647+00','2026-06-14 14:01:08.116507+00',null,null,null);
