[Q5] would have to stop believing that massive results need to take a ton of time And that's something that I've already shed as a limiting belief But even more so I think I really need to tap into and understand that life can change in an instant And truly believe that and I do But I think there's a deeper integration and embodiment of what that even means of believing something is possible for me','[object Object]','2026-06-03 21:14:38.507+00','2026-06-13 21:14:38.507+00','2026-06-14 14:01:11.658634+00',null,null,null);
